snippet.title: Prinny 1•2: Exploded and Reloaded - Prinny 1 Spotlight Trailer (Nintendo Switch)
snippet.description:
In PRINNY® 1: CAN I REALLY BE THE HERO, Master Etna demands the ultimate dessert, and it is up to a legion of lowly Prinnies to make it! Jump, slash, and combo your way through this daring caper of death, destruction, and desserts as part of Prinny 1•2: Exploded and Reloaded!

Coming October 13, 2020 to Nintendo Switch.
